Title: Flume feat. Toro y Moi - The Difference (“Hi This is Paint” Visualizer by Spinning Rock)
Description:
"Hi This Is Paint” was a real-time collaborative painting by Spinning Rock. It was inspired by The Difference by Flume feat. Toro y Moi, existing creative developed by Jonathan Zawada, and Reddit’s r/place, and r/flume. The experience was live for 72 hours with participation from 6,140 people across 46 countries, raising money for the Equal Justice Initiative.

You can read more about the experiment here: https://spinningrock.com/htip/

You can try it out here: http://flume.spinningrock.com.s3-website.us-east-2.amazonaws.com

Title: Durante - Goddess - TSYN Records
Description:
Listen/Stream/Buy:  https://tysn.lnk.to/durantegodesscoldts

Read before listening: We're really proud to announce the start of something new for us, 'TSYN Records'.
There is a lot to say about our vision for our very own label, but in short, you need to know that this isn't the expected "label version" of the youtube channel. While on the channel, we want to promote beautiful music to all type of ears, here it's more about pushing artist that have no compromise in creativity and in which I personally believe in, to ears that are willing to accept that music into their life. 

This isn't exactly "the sound you need", but more "the sound we love, the sound I want to release, and push to anyone that'd like to give a listen". It doesn't matter how many people enjoy it or who it will please.
if you don't enjoy it, it's alright. 
With that said, I do still hope you'll enjoy our first release as much as I do. We're so proud to host Durante's very first EP, 'Goddess / Cold'. ♥♥♥

Title: FKJ - Better Give U Up
Description:
FKJ is definitely one of my favorite musician on the channel, and it looks like i'll have to add "/singer" to this statement. 
Yes, Better Give U Up is FKJ's first public production where he's adding his soothing voice over his instrumental. As if he wasn't talented enough already. Buy and support the artist:

and outrun your fate

Title: The Geek x Vrv - Waves (Official Music Video)
Description:
Buy and Support the artists: http://smarturl.it/OnAndOn101
The two French artists The Geek x Vrv reveal their new music video for “Waves”, released on the On and On - 1Ø1 compilation, entirely made with Soundcloud comments. The song has been posted on Soundcloud and the dedicated website whereby the band has been able to gather more than 200 comments in a few hours, one for each second of the song.  

Using Soundcloud viral power, the music supervision agency BCKSTG and the digital film company KILLDEATH shot each second and comment of the track through different “creative sequences” using: paper, animation, craft or various objects, clothes, toys, food, or themselves, turning this music video into the first clip made entirely with Soundcloud comments ever. 

Credits: 

Agency : KILLDEATH x BCKSTG (Fred & Farid Group)
Creative Director : Jason Freites 
Copywriter : Souleman Diallo 
Art Director : Yann Le Dluz
Digital producers : Jim Tran, Emmanuel Clavier
Advertiser supervisors : Yann Nedelec, Lucile Gautier
Account supervisors : Leo Copet, Robin Riccitiello

Production : KILLDEATH (Robin Demoucron)
Film director : KILLDEATH
Post-production : FIRM (Manuel Beard)

Music : The Geek x Vrv - Waves

Title: TheSoundYouNeed Paris Festival 2015 - Aftermovie
Description:
TSYN Paris Festival 15/03/2015

This is the aftermovie of our first festival in Paris which happened last march with 34 artists and a total of 50 hours of music in 4 of the best beautiful venues. It was an amazing experience and the beginning of something new, and we're very thankful to everyone who came, the artists who performed, and all the volunteers. 
See you next time !

Line-up:

Duke Dumont / Tchami / Rustie / Bondax / Fakear / Jabberwocky / Waze & Odyssey / Bodhi / Cherokee / Moon Boots / Zimmer / Dream Koala / ZES / Sam Gellaitry / Point Point / Tourist / Wayward / TCTS / The Geek x Vrv / LeMarquis / Kaasi / TÂCHES / De$ignated / Ambassadeurs / SG Lewis / Les Gordon / Durante / Ekali / Salute / Saje / Crayon / Douchka / Les Petits Bruits /

Verse 1:

I recall it as the 3rd time we met, my heart recollects
The way I held you close and counted each breath
As we slept, I dreamt about possible outcomes
Of this situation, but it's quite probable that my doubts run
UNBOUND -- due to my lack of confidence
But if I chose to do nothing, I would've regretted the consequence
Of NOT seizing the moment for Affection's chance
So I basque in the attraction of the connection's Romance
My soul dances to the vibrant rhythms of your Heart
I'd like to B-Boy in the emotion that has now driven my Art
To keep me up late nights, simply reminiscing
Perplexed at how a single night can still keep me wishing
That time could've just stopped for the both of us
My hopes adjust that we're willing to share devoted trust
To each other, my speech stutters at your mere mention
Cause having you wrapped in my arms is Beyond Comprehension... !
 

Chorus:

I marvel at the stars and feel my Heart overflow

I find a Peace of Mind anytime that you are near me

It was the softest blanket in the world covering your bodice

Upon the couch, the middle of this little apartment
Thinking that you were an illusion, a riddle which my Heart sent
From a dream but it seems it was actually reality
As if were elevated ...atop a starlit canopy
Closer we shifted, bodies beautifully fitted
The comfort was abundant, fluttering as Unity was gifted
Interest twisted us closer to melanin touch
My lips kissed your nape shaping lovely adrenaline rush
Sentiments clutched you closely juxtaposed horizontal
Launching me along constellations astronomical
Distances, my fingertips passionately paint your curves
Cause my Heart's perception is beyond any collection of words
For I held you against me as I discovered how the Stars speak
To whisper sweet nothings along pulsing movements of your Heartbeat
 
Verse 3:

As if my Heart was giving chase to this sensation
Thoughts of you make sleep an impossible destination
Racing like unbridled stars and wild comets
For my Heart is a shooting star and I certainly wish upon it
Dawn hits me like an epiphany, imagery of the mystery
That is you, views I hold true much ado blissfully
As I'm now longing for the warmth of your embrace
Will I make it back to Planet Earth or drift to Outer Space?
I grace orbits of emotion while tunes of worth are breezing
As the music of affection connects my Universe of Feeling
I float unrestrained through cosmic lanes of Passion
You're the celestial body into which my Heart's Meteor is Crashing
I'm fastened to this fascination -- exhilarated
Being intertwined with you finds my soul -- Liberated
The whole cosmos would fail to bear the love in me
Let's rendezvous at Cassiopeia to share our discoveries!
